00:18:40.822 --> 00:18:41.823 position:30% line:83% align:start
[announcer]
Tsubasa's running

00:18:41.856 --> 00:18:43.091 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>neck and neck</i>
 <i>with Matsuyama.</i>

00:18:43.123 --> 00:18:45.359 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru] <i>I won't let you</i>
 <i>do it, Tsubasa.</i>

00:18:45.392 --> 00:18:47.095 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>I can't shoot anymore.</i>

00:18:47.127 --> 00:18:48.563 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>If that's the case...</i>

00:18:48.596 --> 00:18:49.697 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>I have to pass!</i>

00:18:49.731 --> 00:18:50.197 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:18:50.999 --> 00:18:52.366 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Tsubasa passes
 <i>the ball</i>

00:18:52.399 --> 00:18:54.502 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>instead of shooting.</i>
