00:18:54.535 --> 00:18:56.971 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Mamoru] <i>Tsubasa is</i>
 <i>trusting me to score a goal.</i>

00:18:57.005 --> 00:18:58.706 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can't let</i>
 <i>the captain down.</i>

00:18:58.740 --> 00:19:00.108 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm gonna score
from here,

00:19:00.140 --> 00:19:02.510 position:10% line:89% align:start
no matter what I have to do!

00:19:02.543 --> 00:19:05.013 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Izawa uses
a Diving Header to shoot.

00:19:05.046 --> 00:19:06.781 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:19:08.016 --> 00:19:09.550 position:27% line:77% align:start
-[grunt]
-[announcer]
And it's in!

00:19:09.584 --> 00:19:11.385 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Izawa makes the score</i>
 <i>2 to 1,</i>

00:19:11.418 --> 00:19:14.522 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>with a beautiful</i>
 <i>Five Meter Diving Header.</i>

00:19:14.555 --> 00:19:16.289 position:38% line:83% align:start
 <i>Finally,</i>
 <i>Nankatsu is able to</i>

00:19:16.323 --> 00:19:17.992 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>break the deadlock.</i>

00:19:18.026 --> 00:19:20.128 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>The scoreboard is 2 to 1.</i>

00:19:20.160 --> 00:19:22.530 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Furano is in</i>
 <i>serious problems now.</i>

00:19:22.563 --> 00:19:24.398 position:13% line:83% align:start
-That was amazing, Izawa.
-Whoa!

00:19:24.431 --> 00:19:25.566 position:13% line:89% align:start
Now they'll know Nankatsu

00:19:25.600 --> 00:19:28.136 position:13% line:83% align:start
has more than just Tsubasa
to score with.

00:19:28.168 --> 00:19:28.903 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Huh?

00:19:28.936 --> 00:19:30.038 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:19:30.071 --> 00:19:31.005 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:19:31.039 --> 00:19:32.172 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:19:32.205 --> 00:19:33.141 position:30% line:83% align:start
-No, Tsubasa!
-No, Tsubasa!

00:19:33.173 --> 00:19:34.408 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's his leg!

00:19:34.441 --> 00:19:36.443 position:19% line:83% align:start
[announcer] After the pass
Tsubasa made to Izawa,

00:19:36.476 --> 00:19:38.445 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>his leg injury</i>
 <i>has worsened.</i>

00:19:38.478 --> 00:19:41.181 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's now on the floor</i>
 <i>with a lot of pain.</i>

00:19:41.214 --> 00:19:43.885 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Will the coach</i>
 <i>ask for a substitution?</i>

00:19:43.918 --> 00:19:45.019 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:19:45.053 --> 00:19:46.788 position:13% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa, is your leg okay?

00:19:48.056 --> 00:19:49.791 position:13% line:89% align:start
There's no need for you...

00:19:49.824 --> 00:19:50.525 position:35% line:89% align:start
to worry.

00:19:51.458 --> 00:19:54.896 position:13% line:83% align:start
You have to tie our score,
Matsuyama.

00:19:54.929 --> 00:19:56.164 position:30% line:89% align:start
I understand.

00:19:56.196 --> 00:19:56.798 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:19:57.598 --> 00:19:59.100 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
 <i>I man marked him well,</i>

00:19:59.133 --> 00:20:02.570 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>and even then, he was able</i>
 <i>to make that pass to Izawa.</i>

00:20:02.603 --> 00:20:05.305 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I promised to completely</i>
 <i>ignore his injuries,</i>

00:20:05.338 --> 00:20:06.774 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>but in the last play,</i>
 <i>I hesitated,</i>

00:20:06.808 --> 00:20:08.576 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>so I wouldn't harm him.</i>

00:20:08.609 --> 00:20:11.579 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa, I won't be gentle</i>
 <i>with you anymore.</i>

00:20:11.612 --> 00:20:14.182 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>Next time,</i>
 <i>I won't let you pass me.</i>

00:20:14.214 --> 00:20:15.449 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:15.482 --> 00:20:18.720 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Even with the bandages,</i>
 <i>and the painkillers...</i>

00:20:18.753 --> 00:20:22.590 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I still feel like my leg's</i>
 <i>about to explode.</i>

00:20:22.623 --> 00:20:24.324 position:16% line:83% align:start
[announcer] And the match
 <i>starts up again.</i>

00:20:24.357 --> 00:20:25.560 position:27% line:89% align:start
Follow me, guys.

00:20:25.593 --> 00:20:27.695 position:16% line:83% align:start
We have to tie the match
no matter what happens.

00:20:27.729 --> 00:20:28.663 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, Captain!

00:20:28.696 --> 00:20:33.433 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:20:34.234 --> 00:20:35.268 position:41% line:89% align:start
 <i>No!</i>

00:20:35.302 --> 00:20:36.470 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>How is he able to</i>
 <i>play like that</i>

00:20:36.504 --> 00:20:38.072 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>while he's injured?</i>

00:20:38.106 --> 00:20:39.473 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>If I can't score,</i>

00:20:39.507 --> 00:20:41.341 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I will man mark you</i>
 <i>the whole time.</i>

00:20:41.374 --> 00:20:42.977 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll follow you</i>
 <i>like a shadow.</i>

00:20:44.746 --> 00:20:45.613 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:45.980 --> 00:20:47.148 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:20:47.181 --> 00:20:48.649 position:7% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Furano has control
 <i>of the ball,</i>

00:20:48.683 --> 00:20:51.351 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>but they can't get close</i>
 <i>to Morisaki.</i>

00:20:51.384 --> 00:20:53.688 position:24% line:83% align:start
Furano, you have to
score a goal!

00:20:53.721 --> 00:20:56.758 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Furano is a strong team</i>
 <i>without Matsuyama...</i>

00:20:56.791 --> 00:20:59.259 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>However, they're missing</i>
 <i>a scorer.</i>

00:20:59.292 --> 00:21:01.896 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>If Tsubasa has him marked</i>
 <i>the whole time,</i>

00:21:01.929 --> 00:21:05.365 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>it'll be impossible for him</i>
 <i>to score another goal.</i>

00:21:05.398 --> 00:21:06.934 position:27% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Nankatsu
clears the ball.

00:21:06.968 --> 00:21:10.238 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Now both captains</i>
 <i>are running to get it back.</i>

00:21:10.270 --> 00:21:12.540 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru] <i>I'm ahead of him</i>
 <i>by just a few inches.</i>

00:21:12.573 --> 00:21:14.642 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>I have to use this chance</i>
 <i>to shoot to the goal.</i>

00:21:14.675 --> 00:21:16.244 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>I won't let you do that.</i>

00:21:16.276 --> 00:21:17.410 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:21:17.444 --> 00:21:20.848 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] Tsubasa blocks
Matsuyama's shot.

00:21:20.882 --> 00:21:22.116 position:38% line:89% align:start
[groan]

00:21:22.150 --> 00:21:23.985 position:13% line:83% align:start
[announcer] But the impact
 <i>puts Tsubasa</i>

00:21:24.018 --> 00:21:25.285 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>on the ground again.</i>

00:21:25.318 --> 00:21:26.721 position:27% line:89% align:start
Try and get up.

00:21:26.754 --> 00:21:27.722 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:21:27.755 --> 00:21:28.856 position:35% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-[gasp]

00:21:28.890 --> 00:21:30.290 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Are you okay?
-[groan]

00:21:30.323 --> 00:21:32.026 position:13% line:89% align:start
Nankatsu's really strong.

00:21:32.059 --> 00:21:33.661 position:16% line:83% align:start
We can't even get close
to the goal.

00:21:33.694 --> 00:21:36.130 position:10% line:83% align:start
If it keeps going like this,
we will really--

00:21:36.164 --> 00:21:37.665 position:35% line:83% align:start
Hey, Oda,
you're going to go to

00:21:37.698 --> 00:21:39.399 position:24% line:83% align:start
Furano High School,
aren't you?

00:21:39.432 --> 00:21:40.433 position:35% line:83% align:start
[Kazumasa]
Uh, yeah,

00:21:40.467 --> 00:21:41.803 position:13% line:83% align:start
but why's that important,
captain?

00:21:42.703 --> 00:21:43.704 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru]
Yamamuro is going to

00:21:43.738 --> 00:21:45.540 position:10% line:83% align:start
-a high school out of town,
-[gasp]

00:21:45.573 --> 00:21:48.009 position:10% line:83% align:start
Wakamatsu is going to study
industrial engineering

00:21:48.042 --> 00:21:49.309 position:33% line:83% align:start
-elsewhere.
-Yeah.

00:21:49.342 --> 00:21:51.679 position:19% line:83% align:start
And Kondo will go back
to his parent's farm

00:21:51.712 --> 00:21:53.748 position:33% line:83% align:start
to take over
the family business.

00:21:53.781 --> 00:21:54.782 position:30% line:89% align:start
I am, captain.

00:21:54.816 --> 00:21:57.685 position:10% line:83% align:start
We've been playing together
since elementary.

00:21:57.718 --> 00:21:59.854 position:16% line:83% align:start
Once we're finished with
the national tournament,

00:21:59.887 --> 00:22:02.455 position:24% line:83% align:start
each of us will go
his separate way.

00:22:02.489 --> 00:22:04.424 position:13% line:89% align:start
So this will really be...

00:22:04.457 --> 00:22:07.427 position:30% line:83% align:start
the last time
we play together.

00:22:07.460 --> 00:22:09.429 position:27% line:83% align:start
The end result
doesn't matter.

00:22:09.462 --> 00:22:12.767 position:19% line:83% align:start
I want us to leave it
all on the field, brothers.

00:22:12.800 --> 00:22:13.701 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, Captain.

00:22:13.734 --> 00:22:15.837 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Hikaru] I'm begging you,
I only want...

00:22:15.870 --> 00:22:17.605 position:27% line:83% align:start
for you to play
with the same passion

00:22:17.638 --> 00:22:19.774 position:24% line:83% align:start
that we had the day
we became a team.

00:22:19.807 --> 00:22:20.708 position:24% line:89% align:start
Be strong, Furano!

00:22:20.741 --> 00:22:21.943 position:24% line:83% align:start
-Be strong, Furano!
-Be strong, Furano!

00:22:21.976 --> 00:22:22.944 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:22:23.945 --> 00:22:25.445 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Uhh...
-Uhh...

00:22:25.478 --> 00:22:27.915 position:19% line:89% align:start
Are you okay, Tsubasa?

00:22:27.949 --> 00:22:28.749 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Huh?
-Yeah.

00:22:28.783 --> 00:22:31.085 position:19% line:83% align:start
I won't ever give up,
Matsuyama.

